root@ip-172-31-21-24:~#

When setup Tools:
1. JDK
    JDK depends on which version you install manually or automatic install
    and you have to chose where the path is
    -> If you app run in JDK 17 -> path JAVA_HOME =  /usr/lib/jvm/java-17-openjdk-amd64